{"tid":761263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"孩子手機掉糞坑　父親、叔叔進去撈雙亡","createTime":"2018-07-30T08:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T05:51:16.000Z","uid":122,"like":628,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"8383800da30afdf08ae05c8949d99ed44bf088a0","tid":761263,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:44:12.000Z","msg":"悲劇！為了撿拾孩子掉落的手機，父親、叔叔雙雙慘死在糞坑。<br />\n<br />\n根據中國《看看新聞Knews》報導，中國太原市尖草坪區呼延村發生一起令人遺憾的意外事故，原來是有一家的孩子前天上廁所時不慎把手機掉進茅廁裡，隔天中午孩子的爸就下廁所撈手機，結果一下去就沒再上來，孩子叔叔見狀趕緊下去救人，結果兩人都一去不返。<br />\n<br />\n家屬報案後，救難人員展開救援行動，但發現糞坑有2米深，救援空間相當狹小，決定抽糞拆牆將兩人救出，但不幸的是，兩人被救出時已經身亡；專家表示，糞坑內因細菌繁殖，有大量有害氣體，這些氣體進入人體會引起中毒，如果不及時搶救，可能就會因呼吸和心臟麻痺死亡。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"a816f54b51f0e0b2cf1f92014fff4b6f397e55cd","tid":761263,"uid":113626,"like":882,"dislike":5,"score":877,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪史上最慘死法?"},{"pid":"1d1d5b8c8f8bfe799af055bad9d35e74bda9629b","tid":761263,"uid":121249,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187b0bf2a372459e7d301d63afd0f69dc6d2231e","tid":761263,"uid":154596,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae535d71900fd699273a6414f3fe8ee7de64f004","tid":761263,"uid":20246,"like":139,"dislike":4,"score":135,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:46:51.000Z","msg":"屎撈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24212767f9cd06219867c4f2461a380b6120bdcc","tid":761263,"uid":67655,"like":5,"dislike":48,"score":-43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"鬼國仲有茅廁 咩年代呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d4cd65fc36476a2895e0d436342a2773a97e5d","tid":761263,"uid":51717,"like":650,"dislike":1,"score":649,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"